Tacoma Sperm Bank
"When the Tacoma Sperm Bank was looking for donors, naturally, I applied. It's my civic duty and I like whales."
 ―Andy Brennan
The Tacoma Sperm Bank was a facility where Andy Brennan volunteered to donate sperm. However, during a physical, he learned that he was sterile – later diagnosed as a temporary case of oligospermia – which prompted Andy to question the cause of his girlfriend Lucy Moran's pregnancy.
